---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Learn More About Us"
  description="Information about the Jayapura JavaScript User Group. Learn about our mission and goals, and find out what makes us different as an independent community."
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span
        class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-700 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide uppercase mb-4 border border-yellow-200"
      >
        About Us
      </span>
      <h1
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight"
      >
        Jayapura JavaScript User Group
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
        A gathering place for all JavaScript users in the Jayapura region.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Welcome to the Jayapura JavaScript User Group! We are an independent
          community with a simple goal: to be a gathering place for all
          JavaScript users in the Jayapura region. Whether you're an experienced
          developer, a beginner wanting to learn, or just curious about
          JavaScript, you are welcome to join us.
        </p>
        <p>
          At Jayapura JavaScript User Group, we believe that collaboration is
          the key to success. We aim to create an environment that supports the
          exchange of ideas, skill enhancement, and opportunities to contribute
          to technological development in Papua Land. Whether you prefer
          discussions about <span class="text-yellow-600 font-medium"
            >frameworks</span
          >,
          <span class="text-yellow-600 font-medium">libraries</span>, or even
          have encountered a <span class="text-yellow-600 font-medium">bug</span
          >
          you're facing while using JavaScript, feel free to ask.
        </p>
        <p>
          Come on, attend the events we organize, contribute to existing
          <span class="text-yellow-600 font-medium">open source</span> projects, and
          meet all other JavaScript users in Jayapura. Don't hesitate to ask questions,
          share, or just relax with us. We'd be delighted if you'd like to join us
          and get to know us while building a better JavaScript community in Jayapura!
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Do -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2
        class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-4"
      >
        What We Do <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-neutral-200"></span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Meetups</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
            Regular gatherings to share knowledge, discuss trends, and connect
            with fellow developers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Workshops</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
            Hands-on sessions to learn new skills, from beginner fundamentals to
            advanced topics.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Open Source</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
            Collaborate on projects that benefit the community and contribute to
            the ecosystem.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2
        class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-4"
      >
        Get in Touch <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-neutral-200"></span>
      </h2>

      <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- Location -->
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-600"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
              >
                <path
